1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,120
Día tres...

2
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:01,960
buscando tesoros

3
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:02,440
en bici

4
00:00:02,440 --> 00:00:03,280
por Valencia.

5
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:04,360
En plena semana

6
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:04,880
de Fallas.

7
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:05,320
A ver qué

8
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:06,360
encontramos.

9
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,200
Petardos,

10
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:08,040
ninots,

11
00:00:08,040 --> 00:00:08,480
fiesta por

12
00:00:08,480 --> 00:00:09,400
todas partes...

13
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:10,400
y entre medio,

14
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:11,240
cosas increíbles

15
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,560
tiradas en la acera.

16
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:13,960
Es que cada día

17
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:14,600
se pierden

18
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:15,440
cosas útiles

19
00:00:15,440 --> 00:00:16,440
en esta ciudad.

20
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:17,360
La gente limpia,

21
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:17,880
