23
00:00:18,840 --> 00:00:19,480
y nadie sabe

24
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,480
que están ahí.

25
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:21,000
Va, que os

26
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,760
lo cuento.

27
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:22,320
Lo veo,

28
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:23,360
