36
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:29,800
Segunda vida

37
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,480
para todo.

38
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:30,920
Las calles

39
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:32,000
durante Fallas

40
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:32,600
son una mina.

41
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,400
Compartidlo

42
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:33,920
con alguien

43
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,880
que viva en Valencia.

44
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:35,800
Que no se lo pierda

45
00:00:35,800 --> 00:00:36,640
esta semana.

